x\in\Bbb R
a_n:=\left(1+\frac xn\right)^n
x \in \mathbb{R}
a_n = \left(1 + \frac xn \right)^n \;\;\leq \;\;a_{n+1} = \left(1 + \frac{x}{n+1}\right)^{n+1}, \;\;\forall n\in \mathbb{N}
\left(1 + \frac{x}{n+1}\right) = \frac{1}{n+1}\left( 1 + \underbrace{(1+\frac{x}{n}) + .. + (1+\frac{x}{n})}_{\text{n summands}}\right) 
